'''Bitter''' was a type of alcoholic drink. [[BoShek/Legends|BoShek]] was known to drink bitter during a visit to [[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina/Legends|Chalmun's Cantina]].

{{Food-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
''Bitter'' is a predominantly British term for a type of pale ale.

